      <title>泽连斯基抵达德国与盟友讨论战争援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/zelenskiy-arrives-in-germany-for-talks-with-allies-on-war-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基周五抵达德国，与德国拉姆施泰因的盟友进行会谈，讨论继续支持乌克兰的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/zelenskiy-arrives-in-germany-for-talks-with-allies-on-war-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 08:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相石破茂称当选首相后不会实施免税储蓄政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/japan-s-ishiba-says-won-t-hit-tax-free-savings-if-elected-pm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本前防卫大臣石破茂在执政党领导人竞选活动前回答提问时表示，他不会对免税储蓄计划征税，该竞选活动旨在决定下一任首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/japan-s-ishiba-says-won-t-hit-tax-free-savings-if-elected-pm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 08:14:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国特使称中国减排是实现世界气候目标的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/german-envoy-says-china-emissions-are-key-to-world-climate-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国首席气候特使表示，中国控制排放的承诺可能决定世界是否能够实现将全球变暖限制在比工业化前平均水平高 1.5 摄氏度的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/german-envoy-says-china-emissions-are-key-to-world-climate-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 07:50:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰对部分 ASML 机器的出口管制与美国保持一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/netherlands-aligns-export-controls-with-us-on-some-asml-machines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰政府周五公布了新的出口管制规则，该规则要求 ASML Holding NV 向海牙而非美国政府申请部分机器的许可证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/netherlands-aligns-export-controls-with-us-on-some-asml-machines</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 07:30:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非以关键矿产和汽车生产技能吸引比亚迪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/south-africa-lures-byd-with-critical-minerals-car-output-skills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级政府官员表示，比亚迪公司与南非就中国电动汽车制造商可能进行的投资进行谈判，但尚未就下一步的具体时间表达成一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/south-africa-lures-byd-with-critical-minerals-car-output-skills</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 07:27:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本小泉纯一郎加入自民党竞选 誓言提前举行大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/japan-s-koizumi-enters-leadership-race-says-would-hold-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本前环境大臣小泉进次郎周五正式宣布竞选下一任日本首相，并表示一旦当选将举行大选并加快决策，同时考虑与朝鲜领导人金正恩举行会晤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/japan-s-koizumi-enters-leadership-race-says-would-hold-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 03:56:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国总理表示中国向非洲企业开放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/china-s-premier-signals-his-nation-is-open-to-african-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[李强总理表示中国将向非洲企业进一步开放市场，此举可能意在消除人们对中国与非洲大陆贸易顺差创纪录的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/china-s-premier-signals-his-nation-is-open-to-african-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 03:47:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国首次以分裂国家罪名判处台湾人监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/china-jails-taiwan-activist-for-nine-years-on-separatism-charge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国以“分裂国家”罪名判处一名台湾政治活动人士九年有期徒刑，这一罕见判决促使台湾警告民众穿越海峡的危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/china-jails-taiwan-activist-for-nine-years-on-separatism-charge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 02:25:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
